'''Badmaax''' ({{lang-en|''sailor''}}; {{lang-ar|بحّار}}) waa koox dad [[biyo|biyo-mareen]] ah kuwaasi oo isticmaalaya aalad biyo-mareen ah sida [[doon]], [[markab]] iyo aalado kale.
Sida caadiga ah, waxaa badmareen ah dhamaan dadka si joogto ah (ama in badan oo wakhtigooda ah) ugu safra biyaha [[bad]]aha. Kuwaasi waxaa ka mid ah ciidamada, [[kaluun|kaluumeysatada]], dalxiisayaasha iyo wixii la mid ah.

